snippet.title: Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney - Justice For Eternity - Announcement Trailer [Fan Game]
snippet.description:
Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney - Justice For Eternity is a fan game that imagines what a continuation from the bad ending of Turnabout for Tomorrow might look like.

You can read more about it (and download it, eventually) on Court-Records, or on the official web site,here:
https://pcloveletter.neocities.org/JFE https://forums.court-records.net/viewtopic.php?f=36&t=34053

This trailer may not accurately reflect the final product. Nothing seen here is final.

This trailer features community assets by:
mercurialSK
Sligneris
in1tiate
jooj11

Justice For Eternity is a fan project and is not affiliated with Capcom Ltd. or its subsidiaries. The characters and assets are used in good faith, without permission.
